  <h1>About MiGA Web</h1>
  <h2>Web interface of MiGA, the Microbial Genomes Atlas.</h2>
</div>

<h1>Beta preview</h1>
<p>
  MiGA and the MiGA Web interface are currently under active development and
  the interfaces and components can be modified without notice. Backward
  compatibility is preferred in any changes, but cannot be ensured in the
  present stage of development.
</p>
<br/>

